reviews.review_text: Bob up front Love these 1990 board mixes that have Weir dialed in tight and all up front. I don't even purport to know what guitar he's using but he gets an incredible attacking tone out of it. It's super prevalent in Slipknot but shows up throughout the show.  The same sound shows up later that summer at RFK. Great show.
